{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":900,"text":"When my first children's book was published"},{"time":2570,"text":"in 2001,"},{"time":4293,"text":"I returned to my old elementary school"},{"time":6506,"text":"to talk to the students about being an author"},{"time":8446,"text":"and an illustrator,"},{"time":10162,"text":"and when I was setting up my slide projector"},{"time":12895,"text":"in the cafetorium,"},{"time":16100,"text":"I looked across the room,"},{"time":18148,"text":"and there she was:"},{"time":20759,"text":"my old lunch lady."},{"time":22603,"text":"She was still there at the school"},{"time":24570,"text":"and she was busily preparing lunches for the day."},{"time":27456,"text":"So I approached her to say hello,"},{"time":29100,"text":"and I said, \"Hi, Jeannie! How are you?\""},{"time":30987,"text":"And she looked at me, and I could tell"},{"time":32557,"text":"that she recognized me,"},{"time":34284,"text":"but she couldn't quite place me,\nand she looked at me and she said,"},{"time":37369,"text":"\"Stephen Krosoczka?\""},{"time":40130,"text":"And I was amazed that she knew I was a Krosoczka,"},{"time":42272,"text":"but Stephen is my uncle who\nis 20 years older than I am,"},{"time":45703,"text":"and she had been his lunch lady when he was a kid."},{"time":48840,"text":"And she started telling me about her grandkids,"},{"time":51345,"text":"and that blew my mind."},{"time":54050,"text":"My lunch lady had grandkids,"},{"time":55844,"text":"and therefore kids,"},{"time":56808,"text":"and therefore left school at the end of the day?"},{"time":60063,"text":"I thought she lived in the cafeteria"},{"time":61806,"text":"with the serving spoons."},{"time":62679,"text":"I had never thought about any of that before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64622,"text":"Well, that chance encounter inspired my imagination,"},{"time":68354,"text":"and I created the Lunch Lady graphic novel series,"},{"time":71905,"text":"a series of comics about a lunch lady"},{"time":74082,"text":"who uses her fish stick nunchucks"},{"time":76680,"text":"to fight off evil cyborg substitutes,"},{"time":79582,"text":"a school bus monster, and mutant mathletes,"},{"time":82889,"text":"and the end of every book,"},{"time":84356,"text":"they get the bad guy with their hairnet,"},{"time":85862,"text":"and they proclaim, \"Justice is served!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":89616,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":93869,"text":"And it's been amazing, because the series"},{"time":96476,"text":"was so welcomed into the reading lives of children,"},{"time":99369,"text":"and they sent me the most amazing letters"},{"time":101608,"text":"and cards and artwork."},{"time":103765,"text":"And I would notice as I would visit schools,"},{"time":106239,"text":"the lunch staff would be involved in the programming"},{"time":108793,"text":"in a very meaningful way."},{"time":110939,"text":"And coast to coast,"},{"time":112685,"text":"all of the lunch ladies told me the same thing:"},{"time":114780,"text":"\"Thank you for making a superhero in our likeness.\""},{"time":118675,"text":"Because the lunch lady has not been treated"},{"time":121444,"text":"very kindly in popular culture over time."},{"time":124966,"text":"But it meant the most to Jeannie."},{"time":127138,"text":"When the books were first published,"},{"time":128828,"text":"I invited her to the book launch party,"},{"time":130932,"text":"and in front of everyone there,"},{"time":132743,"text":"everyone she had fed over the years,"},{"time":134040,"text":"I gave her a piece of artwork and some books."},{"time":136980,"text":"And two years after this photo was taken,"},{"time":139549,"text":"she passed away,"},{"time":141360,"text":"and I attended her wake,"},{"time":142447,"text":"and nothing could have prepared\nme for what I saw there,"},{"time":145286,"text":"because next to her casket was this painting,"},{"time":148774,"text":"and her husband told me it meant so much to her"},{"time":152340,"text":"that I had acknowledged her hard work,"},{"time":154758,"text":"I had validated what she did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157624,"text":"And that inspired me to create a day"},{"time":159516,"text":"where we could recreate that feeling"},{"time":161766,"text":"in cafeterias across the country:"},{"time":164781,"text":"School Lunch Hero Day, a day where kids"},{"time":166434,"text":"can make creative projects for their lunch staff."},{"time":169292,"text":"And I partnered with the\nSchool Nutrition Association,"},{"time":171496,"text":"and did you know that a little over 30 million kids"},{"time":174624,"text":"participate in school lunch programs every day."},{"time":176446,"text":"That equals up to a little over five billion lunches"},{"time":179798,"text":"made every school year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181305,"text":"And the stories of heroism go well beyond"},{"time":183691,"text":"just a kid getting a few extra chicken nuggets"},{"time":185678,"text":"on their lunch tray."},{"time":186843,"text":"There is Ms. Brenda in California,"},{"time":188552,"text":"who keeps a close eye on every\nstudent that comes through her line"},{"time":191341,"text":"and then reports back to the guidance counselor"},{"time":193826,"text":"if anything is amiss."},{"time":195176,"text":"There are the lunch ladies in Kentucky"},{"time":196600,"text":"who realized that 67 percent of their students"},{"time":199235,"text":"relied on those meals every day,"},{"time":201208,"text":"and they were going without food over the summer,"},{"time":203324,"text":"so they retrofitted a school bus"},{"time":205348,"text":"to create a mobile feeding unit,"},{"time":207100,"text":"and they traveled around the neighborhoods"},{"time":208335,"text":"feedings 500 kids a day during the summer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211134,"text":"And kids made the most amazing projects."},{"time":213729,"text":"I knew they would."},{"time":214779,"text":"Kids made hamburger cards"},{"time":216391,"text":"that were made out of construction paper."},{"time":218385,"text":"They took photos of their lunch lady's head"},{"time":220286,"text":"and plastered it onto my cartoon lunch lady"},{"time":222094,"text":"and fixed that to a milk carton"},{"time":223887,"text":"and presented them with flowers."},{"time":226373,"text":"And they made their own comics,"},{"time":228376,"text":"starring the cartoon lunch lady"},{"time":229737,"text":"alongside their actual lunch ladies."},{"time":231960,"text":"And they made thank you pizzas,"},{"time":233896,"text":"where every kid signed a different topping"},{"time":235811,"text":"of a construction paper pizza."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238770,"text":"For me, I was so moved by the response"},{"time":242370,"text":"that came from the lunch ladies,"},{"time":244349,"text":"because one woman said to me, she said,"},{"time":246228,"text":"\"Before this day, I felt like I was"},{"time":248763,"text":"at the end of the planet at this school."},{"time":251200,"text":"I didn't think that anyone noticed us down here.\""},{"time":253575,"text":"Another woman said to me,"},{"time":255442,"text":"\"You know, what I got out of this"},{"time":257990,"text":"is that what I do is important.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":260944,"text":"And of course what she does is important."},{"time":263284,"text":"What they all do is important."},{"time":265388,"text":"They're feeding our children every single day,"},{"time":268777,"text":"and before a child can learn,"},{"time":271236,"text":"their belly needs to be full,"},{"time":273766,"text":"and these women and men"},{"time":275544,"text":"are working on the front lines to create"},{"time":277467,"text":"an educated society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279670,"text":"So I hope that"},{"time":282440,"text":"you don't wait for School Lunch Hero Day"},{"time":284341,"text":"to say thank you to your lunch staff,"},{"time":286376,"text":"and I hope that you remember"},{"time":288424,"text":"how powerful a thank you can be."},{"time":291270,"text":"A thank you can change a life."},{"time":293265,"text":"It changes the life of the person who receives it,"},{"time":296467,"text":"and it changes the life of the person"},{"time":298751,"text":"who expresses it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300377,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302733,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}